extendedInfo.description: 2012 South Australian Dining Guide. Your guide to dining in Adelaide and around South Australia. South Australia is renowned for its wine regions, and these award-winning wines are complemented by the freshest of local produce to create a world class dining experience.

reviews.title: Limited listing
reviews.comment: Listed venues dont have location , so you have to open each one to see the address. Not many venues listed. None for the South. Can\'t search for type , allergy etc. All seem to be more expensive venues. Not for families or budget conscious. Uninstalled
reviews.author: A Google User
